question: What are the titles for papers whose topic is related to AI and publication year is later than 2018?
sub_query: titles of papers related to AI
document_path: https://zhujuneray.github.io/assets/provenance/data/paper/raw_data/A Lived Informatics Model of Personal Informatics.pdf
final_answer: To find the titles for papers related to AI and published after 2018, we can look at the provided sub-answers. The titles of the papers related to AI and possibly published after 2018 are "HeartLink: Open Broadcast of Live Biometric Data to Social Networks," "Desperately Seeking Simplicity: How Young Adults with Cognitive Disabilities and Their Families Adopt Assistive Technologies," and "Taming Data Complexity in Lifelogs: Exploring Visual Cuts of Personal Informatics Data."
sub_answers: HeartLink: Open Broadcast of Live Biometric Data to Social Networks, Desperately Seeking Simplicity: How Young Adults with Cognitive Disabilities and Their Families Adopt Assistive Technologies, Taming Data Complexity in Lifelogs: Exploring Visual Cuts of Personal Informatics Data.
